{"tid":2461283,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳偉霆終止同Tommy Hilfiger合作　堅決維護祖國利益及尊嚴","createTime":"2021-03-25T10:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T10:47:12.000Z","uid":116696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e721f05a79a73969dbf318201d126685630bd14a","tid":2461283,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"支那01<br />\n<br />\nH&amp;M集團（Hennes &amp; Mauritz AB）日前在官網發表聲明，指控新疆維吾爾自治區少數民族強迫勞動和宗教歧視，因此禁用新疆棉花，隨即多個品牌包括NIKE、adidas、New Balance等都紛紛出聲明抵制新疆棉花，而這些品牌都是瑞士良好棉花發展協會（Better Cotton Initiative, BCI）的成員。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生不久後，同相關品牌合作的藝人都相繼表態「終止合作」。繼黃軒、宋茜、王一博、譚松韻發表聲明後，英皇娛樂也於剛剛宣布，<span class=\"red\">由即日起，陳偉霆（William）將終止與Tommy Hilfiger的一切合作，並堅決抵制及反對任何物化及造謠中國的言論及行為，堅決維護祖國利益及尊嚴。</span><br />\n<br />\n中國不吃這一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7f2e2b7ddad3722562791fbd5a62f1c01f8baf","tid":2461283,"uid":361966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"乜水"},{"pid":"a5688b6978c4d2cccb01793ed327e3b90023a537","tid":2461283,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstchina.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87-20210110215442.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=980:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstchina.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%259B%25BE%25E7%2589%2587-20210110215442.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D980%3A%2A&h=e53f3ebd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd8425915d55fe48912a6d84a7c8f21d3d9d0298","tid":2461283,"uid":116696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/p8.itc.cn/images01/20210110/07f5b9769e8